<!-- Section 3: EU -->
<section id="eu-requirements" class="mb-16">
<h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">3. European Union: CE &amp; UKCA</h2>
<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Selling in the EU requires CE marking, which is a self-declaration process. The manufacturer must maintain a Technical File demonstrating compliance and is subject to market surveillance by national authorities.</p>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
<div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="font-black text-blue-700 uppercase mb-3">CE-LVD (Low Voltage Directive)</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-3">Applies to products between 50-1000V AC or 75-1500V DC. Requires compliance with EN 62368-1, plus technical documentation including risk assessment and user safety instructions in local language.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-purple-50 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="font-black text-purple-700 uppercase mb-3">ErP Directive (Energy Related Products)</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-3">Standby power must be below 0.3W. External power supplies must meet Level VI efficiency (average efficiency above 88%).</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
<h3 class="font-black text-amber-700 uppercase mb-2">UK Post-Brexit: UKCA Marking</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">The UK requires UKCA marking instead of CE. CE is accepted during a transition period until 2027, but new product submissions should use UKCA.</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
<h3 class="font-black text-slate-900 uppercase mb-2">Asia-Pacific Market Certifications</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>PSE</strong> (Japan), <strong>KC</strong> (South Korea), and <strong>CCC</strong> (China) are mandatory for their respective markets. WOWOHCOOL supports all three through established testing laboratory relationships.</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-brandBlue to-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-6">
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
<div>
<h3 class="font-black text-white uppercase mb-3">GaN Charger Safety Focus</h3>
<p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mb-4">GaN technology enables higher power densities in smaller form factors, creating unique thermal management challenges.</p>
<ul class="text-slate-300 text-sm space-y-2">
<li>Multi-point thermal monitoring</li>
<li>Automatic power throttling at 80&deg;C</li>
<li>Thermal shutdown at 105&deg;C</li>
</ul>
</div>
