<section id="cost-estimator" class="mb-16">
<h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">6. Safety Certification Cost Estimator</h2>
<p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Estimated costs include testing fees, documentation, and factory audit. Actual costs vary by product complexity and laboratory chosen.</p>

<div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
<table class="w-full text-sm border border-slate-200 rounded-xl">
